Philip Morris Cos (New York ) come start to dey use one machine wey dem dey call aproko take protect imself from people wey want kill am.

Di giant food, igbo, and brebreeze company don yarn sey e go issue common share buy right for shareholders of di record wey be Nov.

Under some kind condition, go give Philip Morris owner half of di company money, or di acquirer half, for di full price of di company.

Di board no know any attempt to take over Philip Morris wey be di company oga.

For Sept. 30, Philip Morris get 926 million share.

For inside composite trading wey dey New York Stock Exchange, Philip Morris dey sell yesterday, at $43.50 each, down $1.

